      <title>欧佩克+减产压倒中国和美国需求担忧，油价反弹</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/oil-fell-slightly-china-growth-worries-clash-with-output-cuts-2024-03-06/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[油价在延续下跌后于周三小幅反弹，原因是主要产油国减产带来的供应紧张迹象盖过了中国和美国这两个全球最大原油消费国的需求增长担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/oil-fell-slightly-china-growth-worries-clash-with-output-cuts-2024-03-06/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 01:57:19 GMT</pubDate>
